  .ms-container.ms-py-16
    .ms-text-center.ms-mb-12
      h1.ms-heading-1.ms-mb-4 Client Logos Scroll Component
      p.ms-lead.ms-text-secondary
        | Showcase your clients and partners with a smooth horizontal scrolling logo carousel.
        | Perfect alternative to stats sections for B2B and enterprise websites.

