    //- Usage Instructions
    section.ms-container.ms-mb-24
      .ms-card.ms-p-8
        h2.ms-heading-2.ms-mb-6 Usage Instructions
        .ms-paragraph
          p.ms-mb-4
            | The Client Logos component is a perfect alternative to the stats section. Simply
            | replace the stats section HTML with the client logos markup.
          h3.ms-heading-3.ms-mt-6.ms-mb-4 Features:
          ul.ms-list.ms-list-unordered.ms-mb-4
            li.ms-list-item Smooth infinite horizontal scroll animation
            li.ms-list-item Pauses on hover for better UX
            li.ms-list-item Grayscale filter with color on hover
            li.ms-list-item Fade edges for seamless appearance
            li.ms-list-item Fully responsive (faster scroll on mobile)
            li.ms-list-item Two variants: Stats style (with background) or Minimal (no background)
          h3.ms-heading-3.ms-mt-6.ms-mb-4 To Use:
          ol.ms-list.ms-list-ordered
            li.ms-list-item Replace your stats section with the client logos HTML
            li.ms-list-item Add your client logo images (SVG or PNG recommended)
            li.ms-list-item Duplicate the logo items for seamless looping
            li.ms-list-item
              | Choose between
              code ms-client-logos--stats-style
              |  or minimal style
